#id=1
#text=Last weekend I thought it would be neat to make my back yard more lively .
#id=2
#text=I went to the local landscaping store and picked out some trees I thought would look nice in my yard .
#id=3
#text=After returning home I called to my kids to come help me install the new plants .
#id=4
#text=We all grabbed shovels , gloves , and buckets and went to work .
#id=5
#text=We dug holes around the yard where we thought it would be nice to have the trees grow .
#id=6
#text=We carefully each picked our favorite tree for each spot .
#id=7
#text=Once we had settled on the location of each tree we set them in the holes and covered them back up with dirt .
#id=8
#text=After placing some mulch around each tree to hold moisture it was time to water the plants .
#id=9
#text=We were all pretty worn out by this time so we played rock , paper , scissors to determine who would have to get the hose and water the new trees .
#text=I ended up losing the game and was assigned the task of watering .
